          <head>
            <note type="contents-note">This manuscript contains: Extracts from the Epistles of S. Paul; Palladius, Hieronymus. Lives and anecdotes of the Egyptian Fathers; Ephraim. The Testament of Ephraim, in an abridged form; Isaiah of Scete. Selections from the writings of Isaiah of Scete; Macarius the Great. Seven letters of Macarius the Great; .... In total, including sub-sections, this manuscript contains 48 items.</note>
