                        third are imperfect. Leaves are wanting after foll. 3, 5, 14 and 252. The
                        greater part of the manuscript is written in a good, regular character, and
                        dated dated <origDate datingMethod="Seleucid" when-custom="1127">A. Gr. 1127</origDate>, 
                        <origDate calendar="Gregorian" when="0816">A.D. 816</origDate>; but foll. 190—252 are much older, being written
